"```sql\nSELECT Patient.ID, Patient.SEX\nFROM Patient\nJOIN Examination ON Patient.ID = Examination.ID\nJOIN Laboratory ON Patient.ID = Laboratory.ID\nWHERE Examination.Diagnosis = 'SLE'\nAND Patient.Birthday = (\n    SELECT MIN(Patient.Birthday)\n    FROM Patient\n    JOIN Examination ON Patient.ID = Examination.ID\n    WHERE Examination.Diagnosis = 'SLE'\n)\nAND Laboratory.HGB BETWEEN 10 AND 17;\n```"